column2: select   a.objid, a.ra, a.dec, a.type, a.petromag_g, a.petror5#_g, a.petromag_r, a.petror5#_r, a.devrad_g, a.devrad_r, a.exprad_g, a.exprad_r, a.cmodelmag_g, a.cmodelmag_r, b.loga_e, b.mpe, b.bmvt0, b.bt0 from PhotoObjAll as a  join RC3 as b on a.objid=b.objid where petromag_g < #  and petromag_r < #  and petror5#_g > #   and petror5#_r > #  and devrad_g > #  and devrad_r > #  and exprad_g > #  and exprad_r > #  and cmodelmag_g < #   and cmodelmag_r < #  and type = #  and petromag_g + # + #*log1#(#*petror5#_g*petror5#_g)>=#  and b.mpe+#*log1#(#)>#
